data.title: Scottsdale Musician Jake Dean
data.meta_description: Discover and book Jake Dean on GigTown.
data.text:
Originally hailing from Nashville, TN, Jake Dean Band has been playing full-time in The Valley for over 15yrs. Always staying versatile, I am happy to play Solo, Duo, or Band shows depending on what the venue is looking for. Jake Dean Band (JDB) is a Soulful, passionate, and high energy band. This multi-genre band is influenced by such artists as: Dave Matthews Band, Tom Petty, Allman Bros, Johnny Cash, all the way to Ben Harper, Sublime, and Bob Marley. With strategically composed setlists chalk full of fun transitions, crowd moving covers, and their own original music, you are guaranteed to be left in High Spirits after every show!
